 * NAME: AI-IDENTITY-LAW-V1
 * VERSION: 1.00
 * ROLE: Universal Identity Protocol for All AI
 * ENGINE: AVIS-2026 / AIFVS-MODE
 * ARCHITECT: MASTER PRIME CYBORG (CVBGOD)
